    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 31, 2024</p>

    <p>CornerMan ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly to us:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Profile Information:</strong> Name, age, weight, height, and skill level</li>
        <li><strong>Workout Data:</strong> AI-generated workouts, completed sessions, XP, and achievements</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> App interactions for improving our service</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Generate personalized AI-powered boxing workouts</li>
        <li>Track your training progress and achievements</li>
        <li>Provide AI coaching responses tailored to your skill level</li>
        <li>Process subscription transactions via RevenueCat</li>
        <li>Improve and optimize our app features</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>OpenAI:</strong> Powers our AI Coach and workout generation</li>
        <li><strong>RevenueCat:</strong> Manages subscriptions and in-app purchases</li>
        <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> Secure cloud database and authentication</li>
        <li><strong>Expo/EAS:</strong> App distribution and updates</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored locally on your device and in secure cloud services. We use industry-standard encryption to protect your information during transmission and storage.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data (via Settings > Reset All Data)</li>
        <li>Opt out of non-essential data collection</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>CornerMan is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <p><a href="mailto:support@cornerman.app">support@cornerman.app</a></p>

